
1) What is Appium? 

 -> Appium is open-source 'Mobile Automation Tool' for testing native apps (Android & iOS) and mobile browsers
 
 -> Appium internally uses WebDriver JSON Wire to test the apps. 
 
 -> Appium is just like selenium for Mobile
 
 -> Appium is the cross-platform test supporting tool
 
 -> Supported Platforms:
     
    1. iOS
    2. Android
    3. Firefox OS
    
 -> It supports JAva, C#, JavaScript, Python, Ruby